snippet.textDisplay: The Patriots are the most unethical team in the history of pro sports. They videotaped sidelines going back to at least 2000, and stole playsheets for years. This is all well-known. Look at the Time Magazine article from after Spygate and Deflategate. Howie Long shouldn't be surprised by how stupid it is. This is their modus operandi for two decades, and every game, and especially the playoffs and Super Bowls are suspect. They won by very little, year after year, and the difference, Belichick knows, is this illegal intelligence. That's why it continues, even though it's dangerous. It works, and the first time Roger Goodell destroyed the evidence -- to protect the league financially, and from investigation by Congress. Disgusting. I can't believe the other teams have put up with this, but Goodell convinced them that looking the other way was for the good of the league -- i.e. $$$$$$. Pathetic. They probably didn't deserve or earn any Super Bowl win. Read the Time article -- and that's what we know. Imagine, if they've done this much cheating, what we don't know.
